 Task2 : Create a new File With Content.
 
 vi write_a_content_in_file.yml



 - hosts: nodes
  tasks:
   - name: Create file with content example
     copy:
       dest: "/home/ec2-user/chintu.txt"
       content: |
          vardhan  Reddy
             Banglore
               DevOps Architech
~
~
